title: Register my Expired Tumblr Accounts and Make it Looks Professional for Web 2.0
snippet:
I am looking for someone who can register my Scraped Expired Tumblr Accounts and Turn it into real looking accounts that will be used for Tier 1 / Tier 2 Web 2.0 in future.  You must register the old username for each account which will be provided by me. You will also install good lucking themes so it will looks normal for google to avoid penalty in future. Each account must contains images / profile pictures and more.  I will provide 30 expired tumblrs here.

I will provide the Proxies and the email address you will be using to register the accounts.
